title: 509-F
statement: Error: ("Connection broken: InvalidChunkLength(got length b'', 0 bytes read)", InvalidChunkLength(got length b'', 0 bytes read))

processed.result: The program received an error message saying "Connection broken: InvalidChunkLength(got length b'', 0 bytes read)", which means it was expecting a certain amount of data but received nothing. This happened twice.
A program is encountering an error related to receiving incorrect data chunks of zero bytes.
